      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The single modules available are part of our <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/c4a4d7c1fe7b46d0bb94037c06a9417c}" title="MSc/PgDip/PgCert Advancing Practice in Health (Advancing Practice in Health Framework)">MSc in Strategic Communication and Public Relations</a> and could be the stepping stone to achieving an MSc if you wanted to progress your studies.</p>]]></Value>
